之，第二次衰退将会爆发。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169Qk8CIn3hfteLt4GEEFqEGIEb0XP5t2Rh_57-1eRzMudSXRf46n5vj_6pbN9pyFKFyvcUSruhJiDHG6HlJ8nlWa6QSGN9U1gaQBdyIpT214-vvi2h7LcEEcQgB7OEyztWHTqV96Hol6ePkcGExhXiUKivc1iLSYULeLzYJ8XL1SL0tCztnk4yQDLGX1XZM_gCSirkLUkVbF6GpvODlJ3MQh4CjPmXNVy8yBcyfH23Xv_Gt5aVexr_xWrLZ7KHed_zB-iVs2mSfdqdr43_XEHJDBNGcfUxhiOp1Chqc_01N3fZbygJqDvIzEDgqZFs3Bs2A%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;正如我们现在所知&lt;/a&gt;，他们都是出了名的错误。事实上，距离卸任还有 10 天，拜登似乎可能会笑到最后（ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169WPV14UuSgeyY06GwYLtOMes513kxxqFVKWw2Gap0DMCyzkfxcZgny5eON7i6g83-C_NixfsoNej4cDBk0ef-PpDJbXmWYQ9RObnRbu1Vsj0dJffRVdqQqRD28K5zNyiI7OuOiyJJVWiIHigutt_Q7PTm-o7zdYNu65gwgPK8gwbvWe9-ccPqqa5GLtnyJdyD8w-8uedC2etqJk3_3piaBHX_FVCX4Ci_I8hHddVQh2cifgud4ccHWrlYGXk5dn6Pth1yGddb5bFv3vBLPwIV57n5aBOW3yBhWQMSQF0ZcD9G636K2Xk_75o7B8ipGPgDEE-ObJGZdiodOBlvIXD8Y0FIda0Q0nopvlXKylRQkU4aDhklYaZD1agpv5e7y4aJQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;某种程度上&lt;/a&gt;）。在失业率连续多年处于或接近半个世纪低点之后，12 月份的报告显示，就业人数增加了 256,000 人， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169dlkJTqZT-_5B-w_c7OLxhqqTlqxHL0ZUPXAwJQF9kfS-Tg7G9nxnlygxK7Fla3N6L24pnEtMLtjMlyoMGzSCpMlPwsfx5izMXE5pXvry314H2VdDCsPT6Usd9ebOc9z1z3R6N5olkV4T31IxutrqMyqJE2TcUZlYkw4ekNUZUB6cCt14EcotZkglcDGYwjRFIy3gx6DgRyWCw6HPg9Ie2f7LFKmRxw_YtXOO9xVo2TZZd5FBkY1F011eS8cnvrBM4BsmgLyEzMNCRfGm_wZNFVK8ylr0VCX4hOwWVxthSPMUSGsXCy_cLoYRrYr_XPKwA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;这是自 3 月份以来的最大增幅&lt;/a&gt;，超过了彭博社经济学家调查中&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169Z2cxw2OiQUnm8gen9YEQssEjvBfXlRwbV-gOUHI16ZKFAS5xiN_JfNpTM7ox11bqx6apxXMDuFWS2peyF2oz6F2JIFQ3O2hcMbE0eLqmtGmdhSKLHW7rEkr9A6qUp8UjNa6gC5n2GSu1vwkGxaSEcsB7pwE2L2n5DJP4aeeOf1f3o1aDwXodDmzo2sNMotdAQMZIRKh8iHJ2jRvdfazS4p8VkjypioDjdnhnQdT8K2Fm9DniiiQWZtg863BvmPpATrwruBNlJdtxxG7VhEk_mzuVj55Ku7Yx2tlskd80LvBXLwYReaSV51J4iOl44UI6Q%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;除一名预测外的所有预测&lt;/a&gt;。失业率实际上下降至 4.1%，而平均时薪则上升。芝加哥联储行长奥斯坦·古尔斯&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169WHVmQ3iNpwMV2X0n9Q9eHj0LYZ_cZ6yp5rYDNcBbD-TmixXAyGiOexQCZMl7XnvqR7UIw5-KzyVbY5nWBu39t8LvV1WxxC6QAQ4ZN0Rk3LEWc8rR2Yj6Fv23Cnu3nQiHlwAeEYFVxDJ18ECUVDuAx5oUFFNHnMEWjP29OjNFvwph73hN55fqpzFXxJy3oJ_zoPEFvE8B1ncXS9cNY2286gHqy1SuXyVmWMeACii0XEUBQuhhkRfsu2P_rvGpjxRmWiFllSYLXYAKgf681bwQhihMzIdUmouVOa7EwtqQM7kNMLDZIVRF_qDBRjYfQxRTg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;比表示，&lt;/a&gt;招聘的强劲并不表明经济过热，他仍然预计未来 12 至 18 个月的利率将“稍微低一些”——只要通胀不发生变化更高。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169dlkJTqZT-_5B-w_c7OLxhqU9oATNsRX6wQrvmbGKE2jN-A5UlhYiNFUaD4EAI3Lwu4N-mu4UPMKergDm4KreT_pi3vUjQkQHr0pjTkJbP0ct0ev0XOOd5QXGHGNijQnjeULAjaXuHpVRrbM3203VdXngjTptVyKAdo-_wSNhIEDSzMSMoKtiqbETUiGzECwq08O-aOZUuY3svyivFSH5T46U3yds133QeA9aiVxIsNsLQpI3iHSp3Lsy98CqvbCHrU2wc2LhUtnSfnaE2wIu2YBQPUWshiaZxinC41tLpcU6SsmkOQn3I6WvT3EyaMccQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ibRXGH92tSnk/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ibRXGH92tSnk/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;但对于美国工人来说，好消息&lt;/strong&gt;往往是华尔街最不想要的。特别是当投资者和公司对&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169V_Bz8J2akc6NHosTwn4u-Y2UPy0KlfiMn_3ekSjGtUeQGkYS0mKg7e2walZCr0TssqbtPoOHx7_DgPapYr-WJEr9KuTWI71Dn5hfkDWSxLVUbKWDNuHrIa1elJfT4WwWqgVwcaH46477LzelfOJEypCUsEG9Uu0jXhvdMYDfeR4oecGbGkxhx4Q5u__Fx3NAywo1sWlN1TQtLw424Lk3WU3nzDIkQuIqN98zX3bJqSFjV2cBZYP27SR4rEbmQonEaR-m2yr1Qp_QXwy3kymaNpg3pWX2iBGUgkJmy_3BDd440CoeY_T_yD5jJK4NSerJg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;较低的利率&lt;/a&gt;更感兴趣时。由于特朗普承诺大幅削减法规和监管机构，而国会共和党人则希望有可能延续 2017 年的减税政策，2025 年本应是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169RO0bIcGJVGYwQbNL2V018OEdHDFXfL9YN9uKY6AL9yFkeA_gbkSQWdyaZldBV404pdYa_FoOdYdqyYa2AzU4BXxITwJCZ8H7Y-ew0lYWnX6CJiHNRz1QiXIiafOQkplQ4JhN79SoRwEKZ0s5rVjXqH_VD5To8TOe6l1kntEEk5pphv26T3KMKSPCF-SXqDdH1W1iTZGoK_gUHArKbiSJBsitDXafgvd-cVNFEJmpV404339C0EtO4_TwWac_U5rNvCm5188Hoidh4ZawXq8f4aOnuHcl8-SxOYj2oJvYzDJ-gGmZwziIXbaimERqgyL8A%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;华尔街之年&lt;/a&gt;。不幸的是，纽约证券交易所的所有这些&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169WAC1QJYdWJusdt6S8vIXx4Ka8gQN8rXRYAMUmKRkohSRkzxnDpLRkrhLkBgrDYbM_1i-U4kn1EnCuxBJiBVwpNBwbdCIByg_4CQwDIHeE51M97lZ_3EMZaU-Z0QR27asyLU0OhRFcP5Qc-uSbRXt1bm91lAEna1T78evzfLTZv_6iMhnKP3FzLTGfNjCvLjrEGhentVbFNrpUtUjeMDoDMLi7Rt1mVhEf5uXu8TdV6lkkXGQs1y9DAfOJaQlL6VkRniTmz-wDWzTGPZYKLL_tCYzAO-slKmw5Dh1NWLbYhE9YL1DY-Igvn8HWHkXrj7Vg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;红帽&lt;/a&gt;不足以左右市场。距离 2025 年还有不到两周时间，轻松旅程的希望却遇到了麻烦。周五，年初的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169RYyd3iQrVcCMBaNuUnI3VpKYoNMtgytNIlRYO4FjbLuPE9WtH7IB9GrOWKgyhAR7VI1SL1B0XkNBLY-lQd1rg-azBIBboSrdrD8oyK4rbY18zDvuOtWhOSc7uQKCbx0-g8y_gCSQLL-itqUPgqk7otPlI3M0Qs4Gqzeu1w0lc2dd1mOtkdtE9P6tr_FkLCYSK4M3c-SyGVoeDSieIXHFeaeFX6MDtJUqijnJXG1L_qHjXJlBzPpsWIp_jGvnlfHY68cXIRHlEqdoNHU054dl3UibtV8TihjunBbRsAYpG6qVG7CGmaUxX2LrRZgYEWwwA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;动荡局面&lt;/a&gt;变成了全面抛售，劳动力市场走强的证据被解读&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169eWS_gSeU-J02jgKV7EEqJzfb-vFjpk-Z8s9diEhrf8yVrVvuZcY_CWjYqhl73P6AszDoOKP-CqnrzYcb2gaClYfYXJwLvZnw1d6XGG9xWyTq0y0jzlHquQSFtuPSC3hS6lBSlTB2TF6eF5xrz1FikUXHzAqB3ReaLEhLMX7duFbgAMD8NJeuPocf0beURSpo5bjHUXFN8li4Og2ESTodusNmad3r1V0ow7P77eWP1elQIzTcy0oovI7LSrxeTnLXcZaNhu_-PuF-8rD0vjDN5mqMis1_1HqVI40oGrHMTj6B15kWGLD6152oXrCyPUwdA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;为悲观&lt;/a&gt;。这是您的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169Sra2g7yA36rWql4rBGDuhEdjhG1BORuma6C-r4SrWaITB-84d9FUv09vLS6xQSK-EmPpeJ4uMeBEbK7MPiQKLn_fuYdF-h-773v7XyAR4SbCMu6NSWO9b5pVWNzQNALHl1rR7s77wV9FU_xT2_oyspl3XUHZ9_eaI-q304Tg6unSHoD9o7HPifOELG87geIWGKc3k_lZ6n6gwwni3vuwXplRIw1ZCG15l-Q7UHcrRcEoVyqhHIoSQhMMcRJuFc2H0XfdFlGyu5e3XSpoRdRHTBpbYm2jD6N-xNBgXT28kmdCoP7mnMVUVYE6sAUnAl8oA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;市场包装&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;洛杉矶太平洋帕利塞兹&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169Ywlfs0gdANiqkjfsv36Qto6YdElmvat5a3jypf92HKvc4I-MUKcELc7YTLPvVcVsldtt8AVBtZzDrz3OS3iX26ei9j9iT9WaPtUHYa9cjtY2hZJOywCDLv6Dx1VEBMPJqGQEhtzjpDFnA5OfhNvAI9D_V0m8Wbpv0jNTvQmtdf866t8-jXdC27JZA5XN05vNmWxkn-XZpDrxORaQWbcSLvW6HDuqkHjqHhWn43imRnSCnk6k-enmmD81uefMHIwKikM0k1zigyWksO1aIopecb4N-4k6Ly8oHjuHH7amRF74e7Pwy-VNtVLAhjb_r2e-A%3D%3D" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;大火肆虐&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;三天&lt;/strong&gt;后， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169eV9R8QdP1-ivvmr-eEX9wQ9HlEnYBxKMrHSdLJeth13laBrW_etpJ6EkPCYbl38c2ZdhXDhloI_B3Uj3ePIGww-MobWiqExpC-3doPAfbs4esoGNWXZtJySqUF2n6WnaU8bP-NwYwn2eLdZJZi6a9F8BP_OD9I1vX-HaAn3X8k7Ai7QxhPAKAvSiGCIO571TAvtjdBZoAo6omCqoxdolbU6_R-L3Pxbww6ErKBlTdYo5QTnDOqrv3XkOekAnolI8ZJ8J7PK2VzhW-72pW-Zf69Ixn7QKKwnxVILwFwCY1YVvVs0VXcokVvnkv1uCyVNaA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;仅 8% 的面积得到了控制&lt;/a&gt;，居民仍被要求远离这片富裕的飞地。但有些人无视强制疏散命令，越过路障，亲眼目睹了这场灾难。正在出现的情况是严峻的：整个社区被夷为平地。从舒适的小屋到豪华的海滨别墅，房屋都化为灰烬。学校被毁。沿着商业走廊，从盖尔森超市到当地星巴克的建筑物都成了废墟。事情还没有结束。这是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169XdnFQEALsCtf904kNRaxAZtxr6vArrgO7nDn5BHWNYaOJ4THqkSKWIQou3FOlEuhaCkivLFTwyZ97I3qV-8mxKQEuMnOlUso2FJqAq1Ng1FMgHvgboZIYKCsP2EIXFBQNBjE0Iz_rwjbonbRXQYvjFs5UOfab17G3eRwjJ1HZqW4unO9vkawUXP58nDe6_1op8GoR8S0Dml-zgxfo0W0L8gdVckuF72c8V3aoH2Sf63qWgYyUWbgZrO6jjLYFkDOBzbsDOCwyTLsHY8mDWO4mCRt12pXV_bkNEsMJ1Fkh2dYQRR4XuxN4ezGgfnS7B3Ew%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;有关火灾的最新消息&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169eV9R8QdP1-ivvmr-eEX9wROPICMZwDo8n6bBH-8BjxyhrWveQOXutGQIS5HHANNrJwXMK_HZgpZJNLYgZoJVFlR9fPjgnrfS-gn7aukH9n1KlHJpPzrrWMQxHPty5QurcrKwgbWvwdGd4l25WlvXrB4a-1h-FHpSS8REC2-iTo5NGNjefpvdYc3gjOz2R7cYg0d4eMOtyQ33AB244DvwBnyKO6GC6cR5BJGp4YFMz3gltwY35Zec9LVElHPKrKtMWh6yIgeeabrCe4gY3rKkH3KNxeIDnFU6-JBYiblwBLnt4bxdPmsqGo9BCKijgj2vQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i8C7Vm0vLyfU/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i8C7Vm0vLyfU/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;如果即将上任的特朗普政府采纳周五发布的提案，那么在美国销售私人医疗保险优势计划的&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;健康保险公司&lt;/strong&gt;2026 年的付款额将比今年有更大的增长。政府表示，Medicare Advantage 计划付款&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169ZfcDdlxhZi2B_fwQEK153rQTgkH0_igU41g1N_YrNG8C_IyvyYxdi7DmtSXYRWOgJQgwaOtML1jFVUnHLonhI1jzOMH_lM2zIkQWtqjqzBbgDbmoEqbqz6qYCd-2XAubz37EU5hNWyxPMRz_b6qt0lpEmHQoFNrxu65CDomQyWkqGUOlZu-lZrBv-ZYpUCZhg2xiBNJ-7s_uGIAhaRx5gtSlq2o19jZj4FqOFxql1WkV0u0hb3Iiuq8T-jWVzvEr43qRH4h1FSPyNmcAyy3GRFLLKNWy68D-1bcNCr0UVRReOUrEDH7zj7M7NxQ6n7yOA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;将平均增长 4.3%&lt;/a&gt; ，从而增加医疗保健巨头 UnitedHealth、Humana 和 CVS Health 的收入。不包括患者风险评分的预期变化（这会增加收入），付款将增加 2.2%。这一积极的更新可能会受到业界的欢迎，特朗普可能会让政策更加有利。如果今天的提案获得通过，2026 年的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169WigiUIYxRiB__bHAtgwsDEowLll6baB7vFW59voyD8TdJqpqxN7fuQni2jXHiBngECxuV9zQNEpG_HjpW84JB1OhMRG3mb8gP9mAnqdOq3ziiFBKqvd_D2KPJrzRHqWgvu7hRBV5kgeJN7QxAwVgh9KwVN3hELzKNzck71RcLMfTtKoVIOxUzKmqZMw_ufh4NnYcgSnIVjmZgOYaU5JvzxP3Sq9lNy4cxugKxHxu3d56L6IdiGWg6nQ9BJ49nwCQKwa-C1AtR6g3lQLJcWhUiGTpt4j7LFocyllcEPLILkf3MlCSeLNU3PRTft2w-3SsQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;付款将比 2025 年的预期付款增加 210 亿美元&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;惠普企业&lt;/strong&gt;赢得了一项价值超过 10 亿美元的交易，为埃隆·马斯克的 X 社交网络提供针对&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169csc82T-Msngo6OkRhoYjysgMiHaf7ZcUFuS2UrpSVDQ-o9nhs3mJt5hdooSufiHjATLHEh2j3E1SItRBoCHhn-KSoVtSOeYROlFq5w-_g60-8TxNF5x5j8a7Oars15dSC7bFsY4tXdVcJ01BipwLO4zwjhMRd81X41h9bjaj1n_cVWk2dP3GNpfNOQ_stmJaCA9wE3h6vl8Bn0mE8aiEFTlruMqWAihuLvqIOF1jeAbvbvOMVfFewl1dBNUTrl89ObXfPvnLMIHYqm_0LdGqxjYNsSkGLGZWFmEwNeLO8hKMMIDCHv0EpHbmK-brF9qyg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;人工智能工作&lt;/a&gt;进行优化的服务器。竞争对手戴尔和超微也竞标出售该设备。对运行人工智能工作负载的计算的需求导致了 HPE 等高性能服务器制造商的蓬勃发展。特斯拉和 xAI 等马斯克旗下公司已成为该硬件的主要客户。 xAI 在孟菲斯建造的一个&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169VWgDqrZOmih14-Q0prP1bhXD1IlGSd0uwUmDkEQTpWnuiE6Ekb-KLGhiFGm0ljZRbNYmfyuLDmd83L2DQ08OesRgrXMMvz-ALv9GiJfexew9yqrbZwOBdc7uXt9YyiKMVn6FILc2u6E4xMcix4qxJZsydvhLmh1Otesy1QNRW2mfS-dd39_9Fxf8e5BaDb_cLm-ouLUABjKp0AvoilTOilrwY0KFXWzoDbpzwlVxsHAnbN7aRQAKyR8Dt2UluA-8xVdUNm8o9r2whwfCtJgIhl-Y5-AnEgBb4v9jnoj3EUeqAnjWbNVpkbGTBKvk11AAw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;超级计算机项目&lt;/a&gt;混合使用了戴尔和超微服务器。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;根据州长 Kathy Hochul 计划在 4 月 1 日到期的州预算中通过的一项提案，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;机构投资者&lt;/strong&gt;在纽约州购买住房时&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169c8rZ-mOaLi35C_QbaaeAbDuP1wnPXd6SN47iaENtq8p5KEV0BWogn2axWSe6nbA2mHCaitTYwbYhEFKndPL8ZY-1ZwOOncmql1Md52eKcfarNR-6ueaJo3RkLL5P1s8EJx3hvr8gR9KvBLoLwHjerPpuKfLMLT8hznMmWmYx63eplZ5srFQHh-FA0RIeeVt-UNp69crPn0G3qOOP8hkYtgZgLbGIMC42b9-TMNllYizCot8NQSRYr359CCf3uYyIJDbLcbSpST7__WaIxEACvLhLdHUlDCY1j2VIJVvYD0Pb8MUlb84tZjAaDfxIBKtQg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;将面临新的限制。&lt;/a&gt;该提案可以通过取消对对冲基金的激励措施，使纽约成为增加住房拥有率的典范根据民主党州长的计划，私募股权集团和其他机构投资者必须等待 75 天才能对单户和两户住宅提出报价。根据华盛顿智库城市研究所&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169Sslet_iZkGQWwxQ0hwzWeunnY9p4e5_L0yIVuGaE7MNiTe4Spw5coUH-by1XebKR80UZRgg2DJyQAEJpkqY3ka74jH1XHmoqUYeuc-LjM3sb_N9tn8o6cLqMzXP75qQrGVhbqJh1kVwjV9fVghEkVHDhkLUNZWOmhexLfsaaTrRQnwqFGqJJ7vSZHoa8Y5WzR22uuCm1OwkitJdb9cjYk94ZxbaONzRPn1U7oBYwsc2p3D8fbA6MOPqYW6Bo5GbBJGFjNn64XxVZ5RkvVx1RCF6jP4BMvczebhG24VpwKndk7HT4TUy--kL4ofGvg9fBMGSYV0ez7rPfTwkrVSKMqhqx9AbdTEDQP0TulfFU6grh4_TJbOOpMf19vWPnbWVfgNXxnMv3-kWvehzCsYLdJtrFvvHHpmLtZCcRbBcUxBjMMG62-wwKjCkfjjKsA-tnnNMJDTguj6qPZmsB8wm7Vbg623-8uKM7MhYkB9OTdLgRK0YvjhVGs81pWkxY_Gfve_VPk0f-UjLVHkGHjb7SWjMRbLwaGDvxtE_Uq_R7P7hhNji2BcV7v2rJ5Ws_RLhSX8Yfk6l6s_Wj8R3W6Co4GWwHTYIvNtSHacqKXrrJrtkugrkYa24siRa4WciDuqFhSm3YrkMHj3BA2mRec9Q4aA%3D" target="_blank"&gt;2022 年的一份报告&lt;/a&gt;，大型机构投资者（拥有 100 多套单户住宅的投资者）拥有全国 1,510 万套单户出租房产中的约 574,000 套。它们被视为美国持续住房危机的几个&lt;a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/news/senators-take-aim-big-private-equity-landlords-rents-soar-rcna176793https://www.nbcnews.com/news/senators-take-aim-big-private-equity-landlords-rents-soar-rcna176793" target="_blank"&gt;主要驱动因素&lt;/a&gt;之一。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 8px; padding-bottom: 18px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=351a6836a740432aae676254a7081393&amp;amp;_e=gHckk4cyvfjC2KB1Zu169c_1hyY95QfK1CVo9C2l691FvaxrqyxIevP3WNbBR5-XZtLind8dLxwpUNwMiIIC4alot5GUAGxAz9mjp1s179zt2IAjTIkySn8kWRJvH7TATRCg5KlPOK3SnkEkNJnDaFeTyZRdR2-1AXz-L6JrcV5BMA9F_MfypjTGP_1sd1MIsOmiSEBoVseaa_rWINDakWnVweQns6PlwKgKBRymtqdVa5HeiKIJgIL3zvSJ1EZUIlo4CthYpIvoH8LIubt5t-K1JGBuEVmxB7D-E5roHDSkktYA5nIOAUDROehWu1OMmwDsy1kmbTAADqC9yPl_Gg%3D%3D" rel="nofollow" style="color: #000000; text-decoration: none; display: block;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iP3ic8BUHa0M/v0/550x381.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img class="email-ssl-image" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iP3ic8BUHa0M/v0/550x381.jpg" style="border-radius: 8px 8px 0px 0px; width: 550px; height: 381px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomber